      <title>你能一周不买新塑料吗？</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2024/07/26/nx-s1-5021546/could-you-go-a-whole-week-without-buying-new-plastic</link>
      <description><![CDATA[我们扔掉的塑料数量确实堆积如山。《晨报》的一名工作人员决定了解一周不买任何新塑料有多难。她做得怎么样？]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.npr.org/2024/07/26/nx-s1-5021546/could-you-go-a-whole-week-without-buying-new-plastic</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 09:03:45 GMT</pubDate>
