    <item>
      <title>农村地区的产妇护理陷入危机。更多的助产士能提供帮助吗？</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/sections/shots-health-news/2024/07/25/nx-s1-5051862/maternal-rural-mortality-black-women-doulas-pregnant-georgia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[佐治亚州一所医学院已开始在该州农村地区培训和部署助产师，目的是降低分娩并发症的风险，特别是针对黑人女性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.npr.org/sections/shots-health-news/2024/07/25/nx-s1-5051862/maternal-rural-mortality-black-women-doulas-pregnant-georgia</guid>
